title: Just Flight Hawker 800XP BizJet
description:
Here is Just Flight Hawker 800XP BizJet package for you pirates.

The package includes a "Cockpit Glass Switcher" utility I built myself so that you guys can quickly & easily switch between the default cockpit glass textures and optional clear cockpit glass textures if you wish.

The installer supports FSX and P3D v1, but it probably works in P3D v2, too. However, do note that I have NOT tested this in P3D v2. Install this aircraft in P3D v2 at your own risk!

I'm NOT interested in this aircraft at all and I'm just sharing it for those who are interested in it. Please SEED this torrent to keep it alive if you are interested in this package.

Read the readme file for installation instructions and other info.

This upload is dedicated to falconjet20, who have been wanting this for so long :-)

HUGE THANKS to OXiUA for providing the installer and crack!

Enjoy!
